<div class="sg-container-padding">

  <div class="sg-title">Modal</div>

  {% for modal in 0..10 %}

    <div class="c-modal" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" tabindex="0" x-cloak x-data="modal('modal-{{ loop.index }}')" x-show="isVisible()">
      <div @keyup.escape.window.stop="close()" class="c-modal__wrapper">

        <div class="c-modal__overlay" aria-hidden="true" x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300" x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0" x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100" x-transition:leave="transition ease-out duration-300" x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100" x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0" x-show="isVisible"></div>

        <div class="c-modal__content" x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-300" x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 translate-y-2 scale-95" x-transition:enter-end="translate-y-0 opacity-100" x-transition:leave="transition ease-out duration-300" x-transition:leave-start="opacity-100 translate-y-0" x-transition:leave-end="opacity-0 translate-y-2 scale-95" x-show="isVisible" @click.outside="close()">

          <h2 class="h4" tabindex="0" x-ref="modalTitle">
            Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet
            {{ loop.index }}
          </h2>

          <div class="mt-4 prose">
            <p>
              Vivamus molestie est id nisi egestas venenatis. Donec at nisi odio. Morbi mollis massa nisi, in facilisis turpis aliquet vel. Morbi nec tellus at nisl suscipit rhoncus consequat eu mauris. Curabitur rutrum in turpis eu auctor. Nam libero quam, pretium non sem tincidunt, tempor imperdiet diam. Ut rutrum, enim fringilla lobortis maximus, sem nulla blandit elit, sed ultrices massa nulla a eros. Mauris eu felis sem. Aliquam nec nulla nec magna posuere tincidunt non at dolor. Praesent tincidunt mollis convallis. Curabitur finibus mi lobortis odio fringilla, id commodo mi finibus. Pellentesque ac arcu venenatis eros mollis faucibus dictum eget neque. Praesent facilisis pharetra orci, ut lacinia orci blandit nec. Fusce eu faucibus ante, ac tincidunt metus.
            </p>
          </div>

          <button class="btn-orange mt-4" @click="close();">
            {{ 'close modal' ~ loop.index }}
          </button>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>

    <button x-data x-on:click="$dispatch('modal:open', 'modal-{{ loop.index }}');">
      {{ 'trigger' ~ loop.index }}
    </button>

    <br>
    <br>
  {% endfor %}

</div>
